{"type": "article", "id": 52892, "title": "一组创新家具产品，每个都可以是小型发电站｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-06T23:15:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 36956, "name": "UM Project"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 49967, "name": "Jeff Sheldon"}, {"id": 49968, "name": "Humberto & Fernando Campana"}, {"id": 49969, "name": "Atelier Oï"}, {"id": 21587, "name": "Muuto"}, {"id": 49970, "name": "Lauren Lee"}, {"id": 22532, "name": "Patricia Urquiola"}, {"id": 15672, "name": "Marcel Wanders"}, {"id": 49971, "name": "Thomas Bentzen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/201805070715382SBbM8yDFH7gvqzh.JPG", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Workshop Chair by Cecilie Manz</h3><p>丹麦设计师 Cecilie Manz 在今年初当选巴黎家居装饰博览会的年度设计师，她擅长从日常生活着手，认为简单才是设计的关键，倘若不必要的设计，便不会出现在产品之中。</p><p>这把为丹麦设计品牌 Muuto 设计的 Workshop 座椅，就是一个能够代表其设计理念的作品。她站在一个有趣的视角试图重新诠释木椅，在保持典型的斯堪的纳维亚设计风格的基础上，薄薄的弯曲的靠背和椅面部分的曲线造型，赋予了椅子独特的外观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050623434549kdlmT5hAcpFEN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234345AUPZus4LJKC7kqBT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.313846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234345NVTwWnXa2G3ilvZ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.326000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805062343458ZVs0QSa6RwFmCpu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746622\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234345ajG4RrcBUP0xWNS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.325000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://muuto.com/furniture/workshop-chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Muuto</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Warm Wall by Lauren Lee</h3><p>Warm Wall 是一款会发热的墙壁，工业设计师 Warm Wall 设想的使用场景，是装设在公共洗手间，为处于生理期的女性缓解疼痛。Lauren Lee 认为，无论男女，人们都对月经二字羞于启齿。</p><p>设计师希望处于生理期的女性聚集在这个特定场景下的加热区域后，可以相互慰藉和交流，自由发声，让人们不再漠视这件虽平常却让女性备受疼痛困扰的生理现象。 Warm Wall 利用的技术类似于地暖系统，女性可以倚墙，将腹部或者腰背部贴于加热处，缓解疼痛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234431wzbIZxYd4ojmeOSX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234431wZVgcXB26hvWAiNa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234431t5YHxdEjJkyWhIG4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805062344317VUvfaLJXrqByZp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234432C8xYM3NkQufy7Oie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805062344329fi1JqEXPnjQG8vL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/05/lauren-lee-warm-wall-alleviate-women-menstrual-cramps/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Enfold sideboard by Thomas Bentzen for Muuto</h3><p>Muuto 最近推出的新品中，还包括一款名为 Enfold 的餐边柜，出自丹麦设计师 Thomas Bentzen 之手。这款餐边柜结合了传统的北欧设计和工业风格，搭配木质柜体的，是弯曲脊状表面的彩漆钢制滑动柜门。</p><p>温暖的橡木材质和清新的彩漆钢门的组合很搭，设计师说他希望通过这种不同材质之间的碰撞，挑战人们对传统风格餐边柜的固有印象。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234542GLiwUK92XDW8VbsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234543dHpPGulsFQSjRX0U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.358714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Les Petits Nomades by Humberto &amp; Fernando Campana, Atelier Oï, Patricia Urquiola and Marcel Wanders for Louis Vuitton</h3><p>米兰设计周期间，Louis Vuitton 推出第一个家居装饰品系列 Les Petits Nomades，展现品牌高端手工制作素质的传统。承接 Objects Nomades 家具系列的做法，Louis Vuitton 请来包括 Humberto &amp; Fernando Campana, Atelier Oï, Patricia Urquiola 和 Marcel Wanders 等艺术家及设计师，创作了一系列精致装饰品。</p><p>每件产品均由匠人小心拼合多层皮革、玻璃和贵金属，制造出多变形状。比如 Atelier Oï 的手造皮革花朵，极为考验剪裁功夫。Marcel Wanders 设计的钻石镜，棱角分明大玩几何学，边缘分割成多个三角形镜面，模拟钻石多面体折射反射结构。Humberto &amp; Fernando Campana 带来 Tropicalist 花瓶，本身就像一朵花，灵感源自南美凤梨科植物，用多达 176 片双色皮革包裹的金属花瓣折成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234634oRYFNt9vrVBcqzCK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234634Sftn0IcylQq5shNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690355\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234634eo2bDwBhXki8vq10.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234634FqAwaiVest8Ijcpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234634rmjyg4d6GwHPBYpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.719966\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234634pmRbv6IiWVkgPuoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.382403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234635FM6k0zp5A3ytmbc9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.269882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Patch by UM Project</h3><p>布鲁克林家具品牌 UM Project 推出 Patch 系列创新家具产品。它的特别之处在于每一件家具都配备了小型电池组，将家具变成一个迷你发电站。你可以把 Patch 想象为一个微型智能电网，相互连接的家具共同构成了一个微型发电站，可以分配足够的电能，为小型公寓供电。在没有阳光照射的情况下，Patch 系列可为家中用电设备提供 8 个小时的电量。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234713KMF12Bj4GoL9Tsgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.802344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234713Tn8h4l6y1eaFiRMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.817969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805062347135Cei2K0RfO4hduV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234714l1Yu39cbOFqLoN2W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.878125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234714UiTAjB1X3d0wbMPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.892969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234714xmALtiYbejfF0J2g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.897656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234714nQP4E7Ap8SG2UdFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234714qALOtc2dvnG4KYFw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/interconnected-furniture-that-acts-like-mini-power-stations-in-your-home/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Gather by Jeff Sheldon</h3><p>生活品牌 Ugmonk 的创始人 Jeff Sheldon 是一个沉迷于收纳整理的平面设计师。做了一套叫 Gather 的收纳装备。Gather 是一套集中式收纳系统，通过不同大小形状的收纳部件，把零散的东西结构化。</p><p>它看上去也像个网格系统，允许用户像玩积木一样，随意组合摆放这些部件。底座本身是带吸铁石的，可以很方便地添加其他收纳部件，甚至可以把两套系统拼接在一起。系统里面的小部件包括手机底座。Jeff Sheldon 希望这套桌面收纳系统可以为人们节省找东西，收拾家务的时间，把更多的时间用在有创造力的事情上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805062348523oEc18tvqOGdAZMF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234852oJPTWty5nX3kGbIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234852OLMqimTCwbYk2rof.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.453906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234853iV0aUN1Z3hYz6oml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234853tZU36osEuJF07nzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234853SEtpbqDH7Oz4yBQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180506234853aXEpUFeoO0lbPjdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}